WEBVTT

00:01:59.648 --> 00:02:03.077
those years when we
were missing the story,

00:02:03.101 --> 00:02:05.863
were the years when the society
was falling apart,

00:02:05.887 --> 00:02:09.822
when we were setting the conditions
for what would become the rise of ISIS,

00:02:09.846 --> 00:02:12.008
the ISIS takeover of Mosul

00:02:12.032 --> 00:02:14.075
and terrorist violence that would spread

00:02:14.099 --> 00:02:16.600
beyond Iraq's borders
to the rest of the world.

00:02:17.757 --> 00:02:21.064
